                <div style="float: left;">
                        <p>
The kelly-criterion is a risk management strategy (or wagering system) providing an optimal risk apportionment system that relies on having 2 calculated probabilities.                         </p>
                                            <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">
                            <a title="tag wiki" href="/tags/kelly-criterion/info">learn more&hellip;</a>
